trans-unit.source: Iterates over the matching parent node according to the <xref href="System.Xml.XPath"></xref>, parent axis rules.
trans-unit.target: 에 따라 일치 하는 부모 노드를 반복는 <xref href="System.Xml.XPath"> </xref>, 부모 축 규칙입니다.

trans-unit.source: The state of the navigator changes only if the <xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.ParentIterator.MoveNext%2A> method has returned `true`.
trans-unit.target: 경우에만 탐색기 변경의 상태는 <xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.ParentIterator.MoveNext%2A>메서드가 반환 되었음을 `true`.</xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.ParentIterator.MoveNext%2A>

trans-unit.source: The node from which you start traversing the nodes.
An instance of the <xref href="System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.XmlNavigatorFilter"></xref> class, which enables you to filter nodes based on the name.
trans-unit.target: 인스턴스는 <xref href="System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.XmlNavigatorFilter"> </xref> 클래스 이름에 따라 노드를 필터링 할 수 있습니다.

trans-unit.source: The state of the navigator changes only if the <xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.ParentIterator.MoveNext%2A> method has returned `true`.
trans-unit.target: 경우에만 탐색기 변경의 상태는 <xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.ParentIterator.MoveNext%2A>메서드가 반환 되었음을 `true`.</xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.ParentIterator.MoveNext%2A>

trans-unit.source: Positions the iterator on the next matching parent node.
trans-unit.target: 다음 일치 하는 부모 노드에 반복기를 배치합니다.

trans-unit.source: If the next matching parent node exists, the MoveNext method sets the <xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.ParentIterator.Current%2A> property to the current result navigator; otherwise, the <xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.ParentIterator.Current%2A> property remains unchanged.
trans-unit.target: MoveNext 메서드를 설정 하는 경우 다음 일치 하는 부모 노드가 존재 하는 <xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.ParentIterator.Current%2A>속성을 현재 결과 탐색기입니다; 그렇지 않으면는 <xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.ParentIterator.Current%2A>속성 변경 되지 않습니다.</xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.ParentIterator.Current%2A> </xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.ParentIterator.Current%2A>

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if the next matching parent node exists; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>다음 일치 하는 부모 노드가; 존재 하는 경우 그렇지 않으면 <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>합니다.
